# Nullable Child Organization Support in Remarks

Make the `organization_id` column in the `organization_remarks` table nullable. This allows parent-level staff (who manage multiple child organizations) to write general remarks (targeted at "Self" or not specific to a school) at the parent organization level without forcing dummy school data, while maintaining strict school-level checks for student remarks.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change involves modifying the Supabase database schema (`public.organization_remarks` table) and dropping/recreating the local database on the Android app (destructive migration version update).
> 
> Please run the provided SQL scripts in your Supabase SQL Editor to apply database changes.

## Supabase Database Changes

Run the following SQL commands in your Supabase SQL Editor:

```sql
-- 1. Drop the NOT NULL constraint on organization_id in organization_remarks
ALTER TABLE public.organization_remarks ALTER COLUMN organization_id DROP NOT NULL;

-- 2. Drop old auto-generated RLS policies on organization_remarks
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Org Read Access" ON public.organization_remarks;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Org Write Access" ON public.organization_remarks;

-- 3. Create updated Read RLS policy supporting null organization_id
CREATE POLICY "Org Read Access" ON public.organization_remarks 
FOR SELECT TO authenticated 
USING (
  (organization_id IS NOT NULL AND public.has_access_to_org(organization_id)) OR
  (organization_id IS NULL AND public.has_access_to_parent_org(parent_organization_id))
);

-- 4. Create updated Write RLS policy supporting null organization_id
CREATE POLICY "Org Write Access" ON public.organization_remarks 
FOR ALL TO authenticated 
USING (
  (organization_id IS NOT NULL AND public.has_write_access_to_org(organization_id)) OR
  (organization_id IS NULL AND public.has_write_access_to_parent_org(parent_organization_id))
)
WITH CHECK (
  (organization_id IS NOT NULL AND public.has_write_access_to_org(organization_id)) OR
  (organization_id IS NULL AND public.has_write_access_to_parent_org(parent_organization_id))
);
```

